## Summary of Modifications

This project is a full rewrite based on the original hit-counter project, including but not limited to:

- Reimplemented in Kotlin using Spring Boot
- Added Redis and in-memory hit storage
- Redesigned SVG badge system (V2)
- Created support for GitHub Actions deployments
- Created animated and elegant Solved.ac-style SVG rendering

All source code is available under GPL-3.0.
